import TeamsHero from "./sections/TeamsHero/TeamsHero"; import worker_1 from "../../assets/image/okumbe_consulting_worker_1.jpg"; const Matheatsie = () => { return (

Mr Tshiamo J Matheatsie

Senior Quantity Surveyor

(PrQS Candidate)

Meet our dynamic PrQS Candidate, Tshiamo ready to bring a wealth of expertise and enthusiasm to the Okumbe Consulting team. With a solid foundation in Quantity Surveying and extensive experience in property development, construction, and cost estimation, he is a valuable asset poised to make significant contributions.

Having earned a PG Dip in Property Development and Management from the University of the Witwatersrand and a B-Tech in Quantity Surveying from Tshwane University of Technology, he is equipped with a robust educational background. Additionally, he holds certifications in Building Information Modelling, including an International Certificate as an Autodesk User.

In his current role as a Senior Quantity Surveyor, he is adept at preparing feasibility studies, budgets, and tender appraisal documentation. He excels in negotiating building contracts and drafting contract documentation, showcasing his attention to detail and negotiation prowess.

With his commitment to excellence, strong analytical skills, and passion for innovation, Tshiamo is well-positioned to thrive in collaborative environments. As a PrQS Candidate, he is eager to leverage his expertise to drive success and contribute to the growth and success of Okumbe Consulting.
